{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"<menclose>","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/menclose","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","hasMathML":true,"sidebarHTML":"\n    <ol>\n        <li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element\">MathML Referenz</a></strong>\n\n        \n            </li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/maction\">&lt;maction&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\">&lt;math&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/menclose\">&lt;menclose&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/merror\">&lt;merror&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfenced\">&lt;mfenced&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfrac\">&lt;mfrac&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mi\">&lt;mi&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mn\">&lt;mn&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mover\">&lt;mover&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mpadded\">&lt;mpadded&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mphantom\">&lt;mphantom&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mroot\">&lt;mroot&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/ms\">&lt;ms&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msqrt\">&lt;msqrt&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstyle\">&lt;mstyle&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msub\">&lt;msub&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msubsup\">&lt;msubsup&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msup\">&lt;msup&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtd\">&lt;mtd&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtext\">&lt;mtext&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtr\">&lt;mtr&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munder\">&lt;munder&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munderover\">&lt;munderover&gt;</a></li>\n        \n\n        \n    </ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p class=\"summary\">Das MathML-Element <code>&lt;menclose&gt;</code> stellt seinen Inhalt innerhalb einer Umrandung oder Notation dar, die mit dem Attribut <code>notation</code> festgelegt werden kann. (engl. to enclose = einschließen, umzäunen)</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"attribute","title":"Attribute","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"attr-class-id-style\">class, id, style</dt>\n <dd>Zur Einbindung von <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS\">CSS-Stylesheets</a> und zur direkten Anwendung von CSS-Angaben.</dd>\n <dt id=\"attr-href\">href</dt>\n <dd>Mit diesem Attribut kann ein Link gesetzt werden.</dd>\n <dt id=\"attr-mathbackground\">mathbackground</dt>\n <dd>Die Hintergrundfarbe. Folgende Notationen sind erlaubt: <code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/Farben#rgb()\">#rgb</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/Farben#rgb()\">#rrggbb</a></code> und <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/Farben#Werte\">HTML-Farbnamen</a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"attr-mathcolor\">mathcolor</dt>\n <dd>Die Textfarbe. Folgende Notationen sind erlaubt: <code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/Farben#rgb()\">#rgb</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/Farben#rgb()\">#rrggbb</a></code> und <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/Farben#Werte\">HTML-Farbnamen</a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"attr-notation\">notation</dt>\n <dd>Eine Liste von Angaben, durch Leerzeichen getrennt. Alle Angaben werden unabhängig voneinander auf den Ausdruck angewandt, können sich also auch überlappen. Mögliche Werte sind:\n <table class=\"standard-table\">\n  <tbody>\n   <tr>\n    <th>Wert</th>\n    <th>Beispiel</th>\n    <th>Darstellung in Deinem Browser</th>\n    <th>Beschreibung</th>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td><code>longdiv</code> (default)</td>\n    <td><img alt=\"longdiv\" src=\"/files/3167/default.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></td>\n    <td><math> <menclose notation=\"longdiv\"> <msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup> <mo>+</mo> <msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup> </menclose> </math></td>\n    <td>langer Bruchstrich</td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td><code>actuarial</code></td>\n    <td><img alt=\"actuarial\" src=\"/files/3168/actuarial.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></td>\n    <td><math> <menclose notation=\"actuarial\"> <msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup> <mo>+</mo> <msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup> </menclose> </math></td>\n    <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Actuarial_notation\" rel=\" noopener\">actuarial symbol</a></td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td><code>radical</code></td>\n    <td><img alt=\"radical\" src=\"/files/3169/radical.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></td>\n    <td><math> <menclose notation=\"radical\"> <msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup> <mo>+</mo> <msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup> </menclose> </math></td>\n    <td>Quadratwurzel</td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td><code>box</code></td>\n    <td><img alt=\"box\" src=\"/files/3170/box.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></td>\n    <td><math> <menclose notation=\"box\"> <msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup> <mo>+</mo> <msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup> </menclose> </math></td>\n    <td>Rechteckige Umrandung</td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td><code>roundedbox</code></td>\n    <td><img alt=\"roundedbox\" src=\"/files/3171/roundedbox.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></td>\n    <td><math> <menclose notation=\"roundedbox\"> <msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup> <mo>+</mo> <msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup> </menclose> </math></td>\n    <td>Abgerundete, rechteckige Umrandung</td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td><code>circle</code></td>\n    <td><img alt=\"circle\" src=\"/files/3172/circle.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></td>\n    <td><math> <menclose notation=\"circle\"> <msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup> <mo>+</mo> <msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup> </menclose> </math></td>\n    <td>Kreisähnliche Umrandung</td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td><code>left</code></td>\n    <td><img alt=\"left\" src=\"/files/3173/left.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></td>\n    <td><math> <menclose notation=\"left\"> <msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup> <mo>+</mo> <msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup> </menclose> </math></td>\n    <td>Senkrechte Linie links</td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td><code>right</code></td>\n    <td><img alt=\"right\" src=\"/files/3174/right.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></td>\n    <td><math> <menclose notation=\"right\"> <msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup> <mo>+</mo> <msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup> </menclose> </math></td>\n    <td>Senkrechte Linie rechts</td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td><code>top</code></td>\n    <td><img alt=\"top\" src=\"/files/3175/top.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></td>\n    <td><math> <menclose notation=\"top\"> <msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup> <mo>+</mo> <msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup> </menclose> </math></td>\n    <td>Waagerechte Linie oberhalb</td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td><code>bottom</code></td>\n    <td><img alt=\"bottom\" src=\"/files/3176/bottom.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></td>\n    <td><math> <menclose notation=\"bottom\"> <msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup> <mo>+</mo> <msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup> </menclose> </math></td>\n    <td>Waagerechte Linie unterhalb</td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td><code>updiagonalstrike</code></td>\n    <td><img alt=\"updiagonalstrike\" src=\"/files/3177/updiagonalstrike.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></td>\n    <td><math> <menclose notation=\"updiagonalstrike\"> <msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup> <mo>+</mo> <msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup> </menclose> </math></td>\n    <td>Von links unten nach rechts oben durchgestrichen</td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td><code>downdiagonalstrike</code></td>\n    <td><img alt=\"downdiagonalstrike\" src=\"/files/3178/downdiagonalstrike.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></td>\n    <td><math> <menclose notation=\"downdiagonalstrike\"> <msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup> <mo>+</mo> <msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup> </menclose> </math></td>\n    <td>Von oben links nach unten rechts durchgestrichen</td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td><code>verticalstrike</code></td>\n    <td><img alt=\"verticalstrike\" src=\"/files/3179/verticalstrike.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></td>\n    <td><math> <menclose notation=\"verticalstrike\"> <msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup> <mo>+</mo> <msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup> </menclose> </math></td>\n    <td>Von oben nach unten durchgestrichen</td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td><code>horizontalstrike</code></td>\n    <td><img alt=\"horizontalstrike\" src=\"/files/3180/horizontalstrike.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></td>\n    <td><math> <menclose notation=\"horizontalstrike\"> <msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup> <mo>+</mo> <msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup> </menclose> </math></td>\n    <td>Waagerecht durchgestrichen</td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td><code>madruwb</code></td>\n    <td><img alt=\"madruwb\" src=\"/files/3181/madruwb.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></td>\n    <td><math> <menclose notation=\"madruwb\"> <msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup> <mo>+</mo> <msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup> </menclose> </math></td>\n    <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Modern_Arabic_mathematical_notation#Arithmetic_and_algebra\" rel=\" noopener\">Arabic factorial symbol</a></td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td><code>updiagonalarrow</code></td>\n    <td><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/6255/updiagonalarrow.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></td>\n    <td><math> <menclose notation=\"updiagonalarrow\"> <msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup> <mo>+</mo> <msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup> </menclose> </math></td>\n    <td>Pfeil diagonal von links unten nach rechts oben</td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td><code>phasorangle</code></td>\n    <td><img alt=\"Screenshot of the phasorangle notation\" src=\"https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/7851/phasorangle.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></td>\n    <td><math> <menclose notation=\"phasorangle\"> <msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup> <mo>+</mo> <msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup> </menclose> </math></td>\n    <td>phasor angle</td>\n   </tr>\n  </tbody>\n </table>\n </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiele","title":"Beispiele","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>math</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>menclose</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">notation</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>circle box<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> x <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> + <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> y <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>menclose</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>math</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Standard</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Bemerkung</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/MathML3/chapter3.html#presm.menclose\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MathML 3.0<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'menclose' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Empfehlung</span></td>\n   <td>Current specification</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/MathML2/chapter3.html#presm.menclose\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MathML 2.0<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'menclose' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Empfehlung</span></td>\n   <td>Initial specification</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browserkompatibilität","title":"Browserkompatibilität","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Wir konvertieren die Kompatibilitätsdaten in ein maschinenlesbares JSON Format</a></strong>.\n            Diese Kompatibilitätstabelle liegt noch im alten Format vor,\n            denn die darin enthaltenen Daten wurden noch nicht konvertiert.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Finde heraus wie du helfen kannst! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect3\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Merkmal</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td>1.0 (1.7 oder früher)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>notation</code></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td>1.0 (1.7 oder früher)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>href</code></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Rel